      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a pampered weekend car and a dependable daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professional touch-up on the rear quarter panel that is barely noticeable to the naked eye. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with minimal creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is in robust health. I have recently performed a full synthetic oil change, replaced the cabin air filters, and verified that the tires have over 70% tread life remaining. The engine pulls smoothly with a consistent idle, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It has been garage-kept, remains strictly smoke-free, and comes with a comprehensive folder of service receipts. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any hidden needs.",
